    "body": "This affects more than just player lag situations (see also #5027), so I suggest this for the changelog:\r\n* Fixed an issue that would sometimes stall multiplayer servers when a player leaves.\r\n\r\nThe easiest way to test this PR is to run multiple clients and then pause one of them by sending a `SIGSTOP` signal (`^z` in the terminal window, or `kill -SIGSTOP <pid>` from another terminal).  The client can be resumed by typing `fg` in the terminal or `kill -SIGCONT <pid>` from another."
